00:57:03.550 --> 00:57:13.720
But when the sun finally set, it was time for him to go.

00:57:13.720 --> 00:57:15.640
OK, kiddos, come on.

00:57:15.640 --> 00:57:18.280
I've got a long drive ahead of me.

00:57:18.280 --> 00:57:19.400
Now, don't worry.

00:57:19.400 --> 00:57:20.920
I'll be back.

00:57:20.920 --> 00:57:24.160
First hot day, like always.

00:57:24.160 --> 00:57:27.520
Till then, I was wondering, could I

00:57:27.520 --> 00:57:30.120
