00:57:30.120 --> 00:57:31.360
That mean a lot to me.

00:57:31.360 --> 00:57:50.560
Sure.

00:57:50.560 --> 00:57:53.680
No one knows who he is or where he comes from.

00:57:53.680 --> 00:57:56.360
And probably no one ever will.

00:57:56.360 --> 00:58:01.120
I guess some things are supposed to stay a mystery.

00:58:01.120 --> 00:58:04.800
All we know is that he's more than just an ice cream man.

00:58:04.800 --> 00:58:07.240
We're more than just his customers.

00:58:07.240 --> 00:58:09.320
When it comes to people missing you,

00:58:09.320 --> 00:58:43.480
it's really not that terrible at all.

00:58:43.480 --> 00:58:46.280
There's something new and improved at the Round House.

00:58:46.280 --> 00:58:47.680
There are new products.

00:58:47.680 --> 00:58:50.280
You need the new dehydrating drinking water.

00:58:50.280 --> 00:58:52.680
Just add water.

00:58:52.680 --> 00:58:53.440
Never mind.

00:58:53.440 --> 00:58:56.280
New steps, like the one-legged glibbles.

00:58:56.280 --> 00:59:01.290
New singers, like Vegetarian Loaf.

00:59:01.290 --> 00:59:06.070
I would do any.

00:59:06.070 --> 00:59:08.750
It's the brand new season of Round House,

00:59:08.750 --> 00:59:11.390
available exclusively Sundays at 7.30, 6.30

00:59:11.390 --> 00:59:14.670
Central on Nickelodeon.

