01:01:33.510 --> 01:01:34.310
No?

01:01:34.310 --> 01:01:35.070
Good.

01:01:35.070 --> 01:01:37.310
Oh, and one last thing.

01:01:37.310 --> 01:01:38.670
Your mother sold my socks!

01:01:38.670 --> 01:01:57.090
Ah!

01:01:57.090 --> 01:01:58.090
Hello?

01:01:58.090 --> 01:01:59.090
Hello?

