01:04:58.690 --> 01:05:02.690
Oh, Jiminy. Jiminy Lummox.

01:05:02.690 --> 01:05:11.120
Now listen, you. It's him, Ren. It's Jiminy Lummox.

01:05:11.120 --> 01:05:23.160
When you wish upon a side of beef, soon will come and end to all your grief.

01:05:23.160 --> 01:05:31.160
But if you've been mean or kind of bad, I will knock out all your teeth.

01:05:31.160 --> 01:05:41.630
That was nice. Now will somebody get this big fat off of my-

