What's wrong with you? Why must you make me so angry?

01:07:57.210 --> 01:08:00.210
You know I get hurt when you make me angry.

01:08:00.210 --> 01:08:02.210
Do you want to get me killed?

01:08:02.210 --> 01:08:09.280
Unless, of course.

01:08:09.280 --> 01:08:13.850
That's the plan, isn't it?

01:08:13.850 --> 01:08:18.850
You set me up, and he knocks me down.

01:08:18.850 --> 01:08:21.850
Is that it? Huh?

01:08:21.850 --> 01:08:23.850
Well, it won't work.

01:08:23.850 --> 01:08:26.850
Because I'm not gonna get mad.

01:08:26.850 --> 01:08:29.850
I'm not getting mad.

01:08:29.850 --> 01:08:34.260
No, sir. Not me.

01:08:34.260 --> 01:08:43.890
Enjoy, enjoy! Happy, happy, joy, joy!

01:08:43.890 --> 01:08:46.890
I'm happy, happy, happy. Not mad, mad, mad.

01:08:46.890 --> 01:08:51.940
Mr. Happy Boy, right?

01:08:51.940 --> 01:08:54.940
World! Am I happy enough?

01:08:54.940 --> 01:09:01.040
Enough!

01:09:01.040 --> 01:09:04.040
You!

01:09:13.040 --> 01:09:17.980
Mother.

01:09:17.980 --> 01:09:22.980
Da, no use crying over Slim Whitman.

