Look, I can't take any more of this hitting.

01:09:35.020 --> 01:09:37.020
Don't you have a conscience?

01:09:37.020 --> 01:09:43.020
Da, sure. His name's Tinker Galoot.

01:09:43.020 --> 01:09:45.020
Let this be a lesson to you, Ren.

01:09:45.020 --> 01:09:48.020
You should always listen to your conscience.

01:09:48.020 --> 01:09:51.020
Because if you don't, you'll get to shine all the beat out of you.

01:09:51.020 --> 01:09:53.020
Shut up, you.

